    bf:summary [ a bf:Summary ;
            rdfs:label "\"Family always comes first with the Braverman's in this stunning collection that captures every wise, warm and witty moment from the critically lauded series.\"--Container"@en ] ;
    bf:tableOfContents [ a bf:TableOfContents ;
            rdfs:label "season 1, disc 1. Pilot ; Man versus possum ; The deep end of the pool ; Whassup ; The situation -- season 1, disc 2. Big 'O' ; What's going on down there? ; Rubber band ball ; Perchance to dream -- season 1, disc 3. Namaste no more ; Solace ; Team Braverman ; Lost and found -- season 2, disc 1. I hear you, I see you ; No good deed ; I'm cooler than you think ; Date night ; The booth job -- season 2, disc 2. Orange alert ; Seven names ; If this boat is a rockin' ; Put yourself out there ; Happy Thanksgiving -- season 2, disc 3. Damage control ; Meet the new boss ; Opening night ; A house divided -- season 2, disc 4. Just go home ; Amazing Andy and his wonderful world of bugs ; Do not sleep with your autistic nephew's therapist ; Qualities and difficulties -- season 2, disc 5. Taking the leap ; New plan ; Slipping away ; Hard times come again no more -- season 3, disc 1. I don't want to do this without you ; Hey if you're not using that baby ; Step right up ; Clear skies from here on out ; Nora -- season 3, disc 2. Tales from the luncheonette ;  Forced family fun ; In-between ; Sore loser ; Mr. Honesty -- season 3, disc 3. Missing ; Road trip ; Just smile It is what it is -- season 3, disc 4. Politics ; Tough love ; Remember me, I'm the one who loves you ; My brother's wedding -- season 4, disc 1. Family portrait ; Left field ; Everything is not okay ; The talk ; There's something I need to tell you... -- season 4, disc 2. I'll be right here ; Together ; One more weekend with you ; You can't always get what you want ; Trouble in Candyland -- season 4, disc 3. What to my wondering eyes ; Keep on rowing ; Small victories ; One step forward, two steps back ; Because you're my sister -- season 5, disc 1. It has to be now ; All aboard who's coming aboard ; Nipple confusion ;  In dreams begin responsibilities ; Let's be mad together -- season 5, disc 2. The M word ;  Speaking of baggage ; The ring ; Election day ; All that's left is the hugging -- season 5., disc 3. Promises ; Stay a little longer ; Jump ball ; You've got mold -- season 5, disc 4. Just like at home ; The enchanting Mr. Knight ; Limbo ; The offer -- season 5, disc 5. Fraud alert ; Cold feet ; I'm still here ; The Pontiac -- season 6, disc 1. Vegas ;Happy birthday, Zeek ; The waiting room ; A potpurri of freaks ; The scale of affection is fluid -- season 6, disc 2. Too big to fail ; These are the times we live in ; Aaron Brownstein must be stopped ; Lean in -- season 6, disc 3. How did we get here? Let's go home ; We made it through the night ; May God bless and keep you always" ] ;
    bf:title [ a bf:Title ;
            rdfs:label "Parenthood :" ;
            bflc:nonSortNum "0" ;
            bf:mainTitle "Parenthood :" ] .

